race.description: Northampton Volunteer Fire & Rescue Services Handicap
race.comment: COZZIES CHOICE (8) disappointed at Narrogin last time out but was in good touch prior, just missing at York and Northam. She looks well placed on those two efforts and maps for a beautiful run under Tsang. Carries no weight today and can get back to winning ways. IN SITU (4) got the job done over 1107m here last time out when reeling his rivals in from the second half of the field. He looks a progressive type and may be able to sit a touch closer today up in trip and from a softer gate. Faithfull rides and everything points to a forward showing once again. TRULY GALLANT (1) comes back from the mile today following a narrow defeat over the mile last time out as an odds-on pop. He looks a nice horse in the making and was an impressive winner over this trip first-up. Can go one better without surprising. BIG BOPPER (2) is right back in grade today and can return to his best form. WEAPONIZE (13) can be in the finish from a good draw.
